Game Description:
******************
Play The Fog, a captivating hidden object game with more than a few surprises lurking along its misty paths. You'll search for useful items, solve cleverly designed puzzles, and play mini-games unlike any you have encountered. When fear threatens to overcome you, and you want to turn back, remember: the answer to the mystery lies within the haze.

New HOG from Alawar Stargaze and Big Fish. Mother with a son travelled across the mountains on the mountain road. When car runs out of fuel in The Fog: Trap for Moths game, they decided to stop at fuel station. Boy was hungry so they took a meal there. Suddenly lightning enlighted strange hooded figure outside the dinner-room... When they returned to the road, something horrible happened: car was attacked by the unknown man, that caused car accident!

When your character awakes in broken car she found out that her son was taken away from her! In surroundings you found a letter to Sergeant Greg Stievens MD, telling that military shutting down &quot;Operation Fog&quot; and he must be evacuated. Soon you will find out, what &quot;Operation Fog&quot; means and what made his daughter ill after end of Fog... 

Game Features:
***************
-Captivating storyline
-Mind-blowing cinematics
-Challenging Hidden Object scenes
-Cleverly designed puzzles
-Atmospheric locations 

